  "3293260": {
    "name": "水上乐园模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 3293260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《水上乐园模拟器》是一款第一人称经营模拟游戏。设计，建造并管理属于你的水上乐园，从疯狂的滑水道到可口点心，每处细节都由你决定。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/fd62cf65607ba0a9826e2412b298eac9.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/fd62cf65607ba0a9826e2412b298eac9.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2e46f673c6411a3d428ab4eb85c4e8c3.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2e46f673c6411a3d428ab4eb85c4e8c3.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2e46f673c6411a3d428ab4eb85c4e8c3.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造自订滑水道，独特泳池与不同主题的游乐设施，打造一座既有趣又完善的水上乐园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/168390bee59a471a395eea831453d27d.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/168390bee59a471a395eea831453d27d.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/3ad3d8c70b68f52587e8d28cf7b5c805.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/3ad3d8c70b68f52587e8d28cf7b5c805.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/3ad3d8c70b68f52587e8d28cf7b5c805.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用水枪喷游客、用沙滩球猛砸他们的头，或是“轻”推一下怕高的跳水客。这是你的乐园，你想怎样就怎样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/e9af81b5588f36477195675eaeb5a5f9.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/e9af81b5588f36477195675eaeb5a5f9.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/1c76db301ab389ef32612f8337ef86de.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/1c76db301ab389ef32612f8337ef86de.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/1c76db301ab389ef32612f8337ef86de.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏初期，你就是全能员工。从售票、送餐，到救援、维修、清洁，甚至是捞出泳池里便便，你都得亲力亲为。虽然既混乱又忙碌，但这正是通往五星级乐园的必经之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/caf04057b5d259ee95d62a56e5f4f732.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/caf04057b5d259ee95d62a56e5f4f732.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/06281a6e8efd082957fa4d7c12b5b656.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/06281a6e8efd082957fa4d7c12b5b656.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/06281a6e8efd082957fa4d7c12b5b656.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为墙壁与滑水道上色，在任何表面任意涂鸦，并自由更改地板材质，打造出不同园区风格。摆上各种道具，标牌与装饰来让你的乐园充满个人风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2dfff5275b3c2117634da21a0edeee28.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/2dfff5275b3c2117634da21a0edeee28.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a8e971ca9cb66fcf9bc60b84694200f4.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a8e971ca9cb66fcf9bc60b84694200f4.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a8e971ca9cb66fcf9bc60b84694200f4.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把游客送上天、把他们推进泳池，或是看着他们因踩到积水而摔得四脚朝天。布偶物理保证能为你的乐园增添满满笑果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/4a698a9d217c00e1f6ed11dfeef0e43d.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/4a698a9d217c00e1f6ed11dfeef0e43d.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2356402d0f406debc5e2efc20b63e34c.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2356402d0f406debc5e2efc20b63e34c.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/2356402d0f406debc5e2efc20b63e34c.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在乐园各处设置小吃摊与自动售货机来满足游客的味蕾。从热狗、柠檬水到冰淇淋应有尽有！美食越好吃，游客就越开心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/91089dac5a54c5c17c41bcee42637084.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/91089dac5a54c5c17c41bcee42637084.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a46dfd9e6ae3b36bb54d122decb0b7f8.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a46dfd9e6ae3b36bb54d122decb0b7f8.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/a46dfd9e6ae3b36bb54d122decb0b7f8.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乐园的星级取决于你的行动，从环境整洁、滑水道的刺激程度、到美食与各类设施的品质，游客越开心，你的星级越高，他们也就越愿意玩更久，花更多钱，或是愿意再次光临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/f61e509a73e5c6770fc343482e718bc7.avif?t=1771535494\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras_big/f61e509a73e5c6770fc343482e718bc7.avif?t=1771535494 width=800 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/ddfdc8515a689035936c33627c89d501.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/ddfdc8515a689035936c33627c89d501.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/ddfdc8515a689035936c33627c89d501.mp4?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乐园的游客越来越多，就是你扩建乐园的最佳时机！解锁新区域来扩建你的水上乐园，并招聘员工来处理日常琐事。有了可靠团队，你就能专心打造你梦想中的水上乐园了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/3c9ab741def5e226068d892ee3717d63.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/3c9ab741def5e226068d892ee3717d63.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/123779798358f650512ddf6c20eb9e47.poster.avif?t=1771535494\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293260/extras/123779798358f650512ddf6c20eb9e47.webm?t=1771535494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏制作过程未使用AI，所有素材、宣传视频、翻译与开发皆由专业团队亲手完成，这是一款完全由人类创造的游戏，我们对此深感自豪。</p>",
